OL,4,C A high-level diplomatic mission has   
OL,5,C arrived in STEVENAGE, the UK's first  
OL,6,GCNew Town, to study its unparalled     
OL,7,C civic harmony. The Orakle AI has      
OL,8,C identified the town as a "Primary     
OL,9, CTemplate" for Sector 7's redesign.    
OL,11,  THE FOUR CORNERSTONES:FThe delegation 
OL,12, Fwas particularly moved by the iconic  
OL,13,F Gyula Bajo mural on the former Co-Op  
OL,14,F building. It perfectly illustrates    
OL,15,FFthe four pillars of a functioning     
OL,16,F society.                              
OL,17,                                      F 
OL,18,  INDUSTRY:FSteelworkers forging the    
OL,19,F spine of the state.                   
OL,21,  COMMERCE:FThe efficient exchange of   
OL,22,F state-sanctioned goods.               
OL,23,C                            More--->1/2
OL,24,ANext  BDuties   CReporting   FPurity   
