OL,10,  UPLIFTING PUBLIC ART:FThe Leader      
OL,11,FFpraised Stevenage's use of underpass  
OL,12,F murals and public statues to manage   
OL,13,F citizen movement. "In Stevenage, even 
OL,14,F the walls remind you of your place in 
OL,15, Fhistory", the delegation noted.       
OL,17, FPlans are underway to duplicate the   
OL,18, FStevenage Clock Tower in every        
OL,19,F district as a mandatory focal point.  
